Surfside Tea SurfBoard & Beach Bash Ticket Giveaway
Dates:
August 18 – September 12, 2025
Where
: All Long Doggers locations
Long Doggers has teamed up with Surfside Iced Tea + Vodka to give our Guests a chance to win a custom Surfside-branded surfboard and two General Admission tickets to Beach Bash—our staff appreciation concert and community celebration.
How to Enter
Purchase any Surfside Iced Tea + Vodka at any Long Doggers location from August 18 through September 12.
Write your name and phone number on your receipt.
Drop the receipt into the official raffle box in-store.
Your receipt = one entry. Visit often to increase your chances!
Prizes
One Surfside Tea branded surfboard per Long Doggers location (6 total)
Two Beach Bash General Admission tickets per winner
Winners will be announced via social media on September 12 and will receive their prize on stage at Beach Bash!
